metadata.name: The Rooster
metadata.description:
Made with red and blue ink, with dip pen and brush.

I drew this rooster trying to release my stress from working nonstop at a temp job during the peak of covid crisis.

I found it so hard to be that preoccupied with work that didn't allow me to draw whenever I wanted.
I felt as though I lost my  voice.

This Rooster is my scream - I AM HERE!

It was also sooo much fun drawing it!
Challenging me in every technical aspect of it - It helped me take my mind off being so busy at my day job.

Dimensions - 3500*2559 Pixels
